::KitKat::

"I'd like to, but half my team is out on missions, the other half is 
actually under another leader whom we are working along side with. 
But I can show you who is here currently."

She opened her link. "Drillbit,DarkMouse,GoldenEye, meet me in the 
main hallway if you are not currently engaded. Famine, War, report."

DarkMouse::
She got the message. "Currently engaded commander."

GoldenEye:;
She responded. "Be right there commander."
